Naniniwala ka rin ba

00:29:30.640 --> 00:29:32.770
na si Hong Ye ay hindi tunay na isang masamang demonyo?

00:29:38.140 --> 00:29:40.240
Namatay si Prinsesa Ning'an dahil sa iyo.

00:29:40.240 --> 00:29:41.710
Totoo ba iyan?

00:29:43.130 --> 00:29:43.810
Xiao Yao,

00:29:45.810 --> 00:29:46.600
